Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carrot, why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came along with you!
