Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but can we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:04:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that! Wanda will be mad at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to cause trouble to\Nthose who saved us, Carrot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to go on an adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at sea along with Luffy and \Nthe others even if only once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to sneak into the Emperor's headquarters!\NWe're not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'll do anything - take me with you!\NI didn't wanna cause you trouble so I brought...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike everything else,\Nthe shirt is not a carrot, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. But there's one on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will they last?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a half day! The sea is vast, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NIt'll take several days to get to Big Mom's island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we go straight?!\NI can't believe it's so big and wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is like a wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be my first sleepover!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wonderland? It's not even an island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.48,0:06:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.\NYou're here now and it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you protect yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you! I'll be alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you eating my carrot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pat her head, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! You almost killed me!\NYou're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can have the carrot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was almost defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is quite a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro-{\i1}san{\i0}, when did you get up there?\NYou really like heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry. Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, make something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NI'll do it so watch the sea, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of you must pay me 5,000 berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our allowance will be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brook, either you or I should make something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we leave it to Luffy-san,\Nwe don't know what he'll make for us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me!\NI'll cook you a lot of delicious dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please don't... Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.59,0:07:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Can you even cook?!
